#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:310
msgid "Barra dei menu"
msgstr "Menu bar"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:233
msgid ""
"CDN (jsDelivr) — sempre l'ultima versione disponibile, richiede una "
"connessione esterna funzionante"
msgstr ""
"CDN (jsDelivr) — always the latest available version, requires a working "
"external connection"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:294
msgid "Chiaro"
msgstr "Light"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:305
msgid "Completa (tutte le funzioni disponibili)"
msgstr "Full (all available features)"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:240
msgid ""
"Con la modalità locale l'editor funziona anche se il sito non può "
"raggiungere CDN esterni (firewall, ambienti air-gapped, policy di sicurezza "
"restrittive)."
msgstr ""
"In local mode the editor keeps working even if the site cannot reach "
"external CDNs (firewalls, air-gapped environments, strict security "
"policies)."

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:188
msgid ""
"Configura l'editor classico moderno (TinyMCE 7) e la disattivazione di "
"Gutenberg."
msgstr ""
"Configure the modern classic editor (TinyMCE 7) and the Gutenberg opt-out."

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:262
msgid "Controlla aggiornamenti"
msgstr "Check for updates"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:278
msgid ""
"Controlla automaticamente una volta al giorno se è disponibile una nuova "
"versione e scaricala in background"
msgstr ""
"Automatically check once a day for a new version and download it in the "
"background"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:274
msgid "Controllo automatico"
msgstr "Automatic check"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:167
msgid "Controllo in corso…"
msgstr "Checking…"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:228
msgid "Da dove caricare TinyMCE"
msgstr "Where to load TinyMCE from"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:196
msgid "Disattiva Gutenberg"
msgstr "Disable Gutenberg"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:281
msgid ""
"Disattivato di default: nessuna richiesta esterna viene effettuata senza il "
"tuo consenso esplicito. Anche con questa opzione disattivata puoi sempre "
"controllare e scaricare manualmente con i bottoni qui sopra."
msgstr ""
"Disabled by default: no external request is made without your explicit "
"consent. Even with this option off, you can always check and download "
"manually using the buttons above."

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:168
msgid "Download in corso, potrebbe richiedere qualche secondo…"
msgstr "Downloading, this may take a few seconds…"

#: includes/class-mce-vendor.php:294
msgid "Download non riuscito per il file: %s"
msgstr "Download failed for file: %s"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:287
msgid "Editor TinyMCE moderno"
msgstr "Modern TinyMCE editor"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:193
msgid "Editor a blocchi (Gutenberg)"
msgstr "Block editor (Gutenberg)"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:304
msgid "Estesa (font, colori, tabelle, allineamento)"
msgstr "Extended (fonts, colors, tables, alignment)"

#: includes/class-mce-vendor.php:347
msgid "Il download è incompleto: alcuni file richiesti risultano mancanti."
msgstr "The download is incomplete: some required files are missing."

#: includes/class-mce-vendor.php:215
msgid "Il registro npm ha risposto con codice %d."
msgstr "The npm registry responded with status code %d."

#: includes/class-mce-vendor.php:314
msgid "Impossibile salvare il file scaricato: %s"
msgstr "Could not save the downloaded file: %s"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:237
msgid ""
"Locale (offline) — file inclusi nel plugin o scaricati in precedenza, "
"nessuna richiesta esterna durante l'uso dell'editor"
msgstr ""
"Local (offline) — files bundled with the plugin or previously downloaded, no"
" external requests while using the editor"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:66 includes/class-mce-settings.php:67
#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:187
msgid "Modern Classic Editor"
msgstr "Modern Classic Editor"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:314
msgid "Mostra la barra dei menu (File, Modifica, Inserisci, ecc.)"
msgstr "Show the menu bar (File, Edit, Insert, etc.)"

#: includes/class-mce-vendor.php:234
msgid "Nessuna versione 7.x trovata su npm."
msgstr "No 7.x version found on npm."

#: includes/class-mce-vendor.php:258
msgid "Numero di versione non valido."
msgstr "Invalid version number."

#: includes/class-mce-vendor.php:371 includes/class-mce-vendor.php:405
msgid "Permessi insufficienti."
msgstr "Insufficient permissions."

#: includes/class-mce-vendor.php:222
msgid "Risposta del registro npm non valida."
msgstr "Invalid response from the npm registry."

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:265
msgid "Scarica e installa l'ultima versione"
msgstr "Download and install the latest version"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:295
msgid "Scuro"
msgstr "Dark"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:293
msgid "Segui il sistema operativo"
msgstr "Follow operating system"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:171
msgid "Si è verificato un errore. Riprova."
msgstr "Something went wrong. Please try again."

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:219
msgid "Solo i tipi selezionati torneranno all'editor classico."
msgstr "Only the selected types will switch back to the classic editor."

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:225
msgid "Sorgente dell'editor TinyMCE"
msgstr "TinyMCE editor source"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:169
msgid "Stai già usando l'ultima versione disponibile."
msgstr "You're already using the latest available version."

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:303
msgid "Standard (come WordPress di default)"
msgstr "Standard (WordPress default)"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:290
msgid "Tema (dark mode)"
msgstr "Theme (dark mode)"

#: includes/class-mce-vendor.php:389
msgid "TinyMCE %s scaricato e installato correttamente."
msgstr "TinyMCE %s downloaded and installed successfully."

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:325
msgid ""
"TinyMCE è distribuito sotto licenza GPLv2+ (GNU General Public License). In "
"modalità CDN viene caricato da jsDelivr; in modalità locale i file "
"(identici, non modificati) provengono dal pacchetto ufficiale \"tinymce\" su"
" npm, incluso nel plugin o scaricato da questa pagina. Nessun account o API "
"key è richiesto in entrambi i casi."
msgstr ""
"TinyMCE is distributed under the GPLv2+ license (GNU General Public "
"License). In CDN mode it is loaded from jsDelivr; in local mode the files "
"(identical, unmodified) come from the official \"tinymce\" package on npm, "
"either bundled with the plugin or downloaded from this page. No account or "
"API key is required in either case."

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:205
msgid "Tipi di contenuto"
msgstr "Content types"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:300
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Toolbar"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:200
msgid ""
"Usa l'editor classico invece dell'editor a blocchi per i tipi di contenuto "
"selezionati qui sotto"
msgstr ""
"Use the classic editor instead of the block editor for the content types "
"selected below"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:253
msgid "Versione attualmente disponibile offline: %1$s (%2$s)"
msgstr "Currently available offline version: %1$s (%2$s)"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:248
msgid "Versione locale disponibile"
msgstr "Available local version"

#: includes/class-mce-vendor.php:376
msgid "Versione non specificata."
msgstr "Version not specified."

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:255
msgid "incluse nel plugin"
msgstr "bundled with the plugin"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:255 includes/class-mce-settings.php:255
msgid "scaricata"
msgstr "downloaded"

#: includes/class-mce-settings.php:170
msgid "È disponibile una nuova versione: "
msgstr "A new version is available: "
